00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,128
Kapan saatnya aman.

481
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:15,681
Kapan izinkan orang masuk.

482
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:22,762
Peraturan terus berubah.

483
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:25,486
Itu berubah bagiku.

484
00:39:39,120 --> 00:39:41,964
Sebelum kita melanjutkan, aku harus...

485
00:39:42,120 --> 00:39:44,202
Aku harus ambil waktu sejenak.

486
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:08,361
Kau siap?

487
